HTML Entity (decimal)	&#1;
HTML Entity (hex)	&#x1;

How to type in Microsoft Windows ( Alt +0001 )
Alt 01
Alt 1

UTF-8  (hex)	        0x01 (01)
UTF-8  (binary)	        00000001
UTF-16 (hex)	        0x0001 (0001)
UTF-16 (decimal)	1
UTF-32 (hex)	        0x00000001 (0001)
UTF-32 (decimal)        1

C/C++/Java source code	"\u0001"
Python source code	u"\u0001
